item.title: Let's Build & Deploy a MCP Server with C#
item.description:
Looking to get started building and testing your own Model Context Protocol (MCP) server? Look no further than the new C# SDK for MCPs. You can build both client and servers with a delightful API that gets you up and running in minutes. Best of all you can build, test, and deploy directly from VS Code.
